    "active_lock_reason": null,
    "body": "As a core developer I want every configuration schema to be checked for correctness during CI tests so that I won't merge PRs with invalid configuration schema.\r\n\r\n### Rationale\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/10236#issuecomment-450804804 for the originating request on this feature and https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/9878#issuecomment-450749931 for a bug report related to an accidental merge of an invalid schema.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nConfiguration schema are valid JSON data and can be checked against a JSON schema meta-schema.\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\nDraft 4 meta-schema can be found [here](http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema)\r\n",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
